    "body": "### Description\n\nThis works, and will ignore ` ~\\AppData\\Local\\Programs\\Python\\Python313\\Lib\\` when the buffer is opened from a different location `~\\User\\project\\`\n\n```lua\n      local lspconfig = require(\"lspconfig\")\n        lspconfig.basedpyright.setup({\n          settings = {\n            basedpyright = {\n              analysis = {\n                ignore = { \"*\" },\n              },\n            },\n          },\n        })\n```\n\nThis doesn't and will only ignore the project root files and their childs:\n\n```lua\n        vim.lsp.config(\"basedpyright\", {\n          settings = {\n            basedpyright = {\n              analysis = {\n                ignore = { \"*\" },\n              },\n            },\n          },\n        })\n```\n\nAm I missing something ?",
