            "author_association": "MEMBER",
            "body": "It's probably getting overridden by lspconfig because it loads too early (where have you defined it?). Try creating `after/lsp/basedpyright.lua` containing:\n\n```lua\nreturn {\n  settings = {\n    basedpyright = {\n      analysis = {\n        ignore = { \"*\" },\n      },\n    },\n  },\n}\n```\n\nSee `:help lsp-config-merge`.",
