        {
            "author_association": "NONE",
            "body": "Fixed by going from \n```lua\nvim.lsp.config(\"basedpyright\", {\n  settings = {\n    basedpyright = {\n      analysis = {\n        ignore = { \"*\" },\n      },\n    },\n  },\n})\n```\nto\n```lua\nvim.lsp.config(\"basedpyright\", {\n  settings = {\n    basedpyright = {\n      analysis = {\n        ignore = { \n          \"*:/*\",  -- Windows (requires drive letter prefix)\n          \"/*\",     -- Linux/Unix (requires / prefix)\n        },\n      },\n    },\n  },\n})\n```\n\n",
